title: #135: Vegas With Steve Greene
description: Thank you for tuning in for another Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli.  This episode we welcome back from the "Sh*t They Don't Tell You Podcast," Steve Greene, to revisit Las Vegas. Please enjoy a podcast of three men yelling at each other in mutual agreement. Thank you so much for all of your support.
